FBIS3-14417 "drnes059_l_94004" FBIS-NES-94-059 Document Type:Daily Report 28 Mar 1994 ISRAEL Minister Aloni on Golan, Syria TA2803122394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in Hebrew 1200 GMT 28 Mar 94 TA2803122394 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el Language: Hebrew Article Type:BFN [Text] Minister Shulamit Aloni says the people of Israel must adjust to the idea that they will have to be separated from the Golan, because it is Syrian land. She made these remarks during the inaugural broadcast of Qol Yisra'el's Qol Kineret radio station.
